'''咪达唑仑'''（[[INN|INN]]：'''Midazolam'''，商品名为'''Versed'''）是一种[[苯二氮卓类|苯二氮卓类]]药物，用于[[麻醉|麻醉]]、[[程序性镇静和镇痛|程序性镇静]]、[[失眠|睡眠困难]]和[[精神运动性激动|严重躁动]]。<ref name="ashp">{{Cite web |title=Midazolam Monograph for Professionals |url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/midazolam.html |publisher=American Society of Health-System Pharmacists |website=Drugs.com |language=en |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>它通过诱导嗜睡、减少焦虑和导致[[顺行性遗忘症|失去创造新记忆的能力]]而起作用。该药物不会使人失去知觉，而只是被镇静。<ref name="ashp" />它也可用于治疗长时间（持续超过5分钟）的[[癫痫发作|癫痫发作]]。<ref name="epilepsybehavior">{{Cite journal |last=Brigo |first=Francesco |last2=Nardone |first2=Raffaele |last3=Tezzon |first3=Frediano |last4=Trinka |first4=Eugen |date=2015-08 |title=Nonintravenous midazolam versus intravenous or rectal diazepam for the treatment of early status epilepticus: A systematic review with meta-analysis |url=https://www.epilepsybehavior.com/article/S1525-5050(15)00090-6/fulltext |journal=Epilepsy & Behavior: E&B |volume=49 |doi=10.1016/j.yebeh.2015.02.030 |issn=1525-5069 |pmid=25817929}}</ref>咪达唑仑可以[[口服给药|口服]]、[[静脉注射|静脉注射]]、[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]、[[鼻腔给药|喷入鼻子]]或通过[[颊部给药|颊部给药]]。<ref name="ashp" /><ref name="epilepsybehavior" />静脉注射时，它通常在五分钟内开始起作用； 注射到肌肉中时，可能需要十五分钟才能开始工作。<ref name="ashp" />效果持续一到六个小时。

副作用可能包括呼吸困难、[[低血压|低血压]]和嗜睡。<ref name="ashp" />长期使用后可能会出现对其影响的[[药物耐受性|耐受性]]和[[苯二氮䓬类药物停药综合征|戒断综合征]]。<ref name="wiley">{{Cite journal |last=Riss |first=J. |last2=Cloyd |first2=J. |last3=Gates |first3=J. |last4=Collins |first4=S. |date=2008-08 |title=Benzodiazepines in epilepsy: pharmacology and pharmacokinetics |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1600-0404.2008.01004.x |journal=Acta Neurologica Scandinavica |language=en |volume=118 |issue=2 |doi=10.1111/j.1600-0404.2008.01004.x |issn=1600-0404 |pmid=18384456}}</ref>特别是在儿童和老年人身上可能会出现[[反常反应|反常反应]]，例如活动增加。<ref name="wiley" />有证据表明在怀孕期间使用有风险，但没有证据表明在[[母乳哺育|母乳喂养]]期间单次服用会造成伤害。<ref name="worldcat">{{Cite book|title=Tarascon pocket pharmacopoeia 2015 deluxe lab coat edition.|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/922644939|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|date=2014|location=Sudbury|isbn=1-284-05756-9|oclc=922644939}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Midazolam use while Breastfeeding |url=https://www.drugs.com/breastfeeding/midazolam.html |website=Drugs.com |language=en |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>它属于苯二氮卓类药物，通过增加大脑中[[γ-氨基丁酸|GABA神经递质]]的活性起作用。<ref name="ashp" />

咪达唑仑于1974年获得专利，并于1982年进入医疗用途。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Analogue-based drug discovery|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/77601762|publisher=Wiley-VCH|date=2006|location=Weinheim|isbn=978-3-527-60749-5|oclc=77601762|first=János|last=Fischer|first2=C. R.|last2=Ganellin}}</ref>它在[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]上。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=World Health Organization |date=2019 |title=World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 |url=https://apps.who.int/iris/handle/10665/325771 |hdl=10665/325771 |language=en}}</ref>咪达唑仑可作为[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]使用。<ref name="worldcat" />在许多国家，它是一种[[管制药物|管制药物]]。<ref name="ashp" />

== 医疗用途 ==
=== 癫痫发作 ===
咪达唑仑有时用于长时间癫痫发作的急性治疗。不推荐长期用于治疗癫痫，因为存在显著的耐受风险（导致咪达唑仑和其他苯二氮卓类药物无效）以及镇静剂的显著副作用。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Isojärvi |first=J. I. |last2=Tokola |first2=R. A. |date=1998-12 |title=Benzodiazepines in the treatment of epilepsy in people with intellectual disability |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10030438 |journal=Journal of intellectual disability research: JIDR |volume=42 Suppl 1 |issn=0964-2633 |pmid=10030438}}</ref>咪达唑仑的一个好处是，在儿童中，它可以在面颊或鼻子中用于治疗急性癫痫发作，包括[[癫痫重积状态|癫痫重积状态]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=McTague |first=Amy |last2=Martland |first2=Timothy |last3=Appleton |first3=Richard |date=2018-01-10 |editor-last=Cochrane Epilepsy Group |title=Drug management for acute tonic-clonic convulsions including convulsive status epilepticus in children |url=https://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/14651858.CD001905.pub3 |journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |language=en |volume=2018 |issue=1 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001905.pub3 |pmc=PMC6491279 |pmid=29320603}}</ref><ref name="bmj">{{Cite journal |last=Walker |first=Matthew |date=2005-09-22 |title=Status epilepticus: an evidence based guide |url=https://www.bmj.com/content/331/7518/673 |journal=BMJ |language=en |volume=331 |issue=7518 |doi=10.1136/bmj.331.7518.673 |issn=0959-8138 |pmc=1226249 |pmid=16179702}}</ref>咪达唑仑对癫痫重积状态或无法获得静脉通路时有效，并且与其他苯二氮卓类药物一样具有水溶性、起效迅速且不会引起[[1,2-丙二醇|丙二醇]]载体[[代谢性酸中毒|代谢性酸中毒]]（由于其溶于水，因此不需要）的优点。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=McMullan |first=Jason |last2=Sasson |first2=Comilla |last3=Pancioli |first3=Arthur |last4=Silbergleit |first4=Robert |date=2010-06 |title=Midazolam versus diazepam for the treatment of status epilepticus in children and young adults: a meta-analysis |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1553-2712.2010.00751.x |journal=Academic Emergency Medicine: Official Journal of the Society for Academic Emergency Medicine |volume=17 |issue=6 |doi=10.1111/j.1553-2712.2010.00751.x |issn=1553-2712 |pmc=4149412 |pmid=20624136}}</ref>

缺点包括超过50%的接受治疗的人因咪达唑仑的半衰期短而发生癫痫大发作，以及14－18%的难治性癫痫重积状态患者治疗失败。对抗惊厥作用的耐受性迅速发展，可能需要将剂量增加数倍以维持抗惊厥治疗效果。长时间使用，可能会出现耐受性和[[快速耐受|快速耐受]]，并且消除半衰期可能会增加，长达数天。<ref name="wiley" /><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Murthy |first=J. M. K. |date=2006-10-01 |title=Refractory status epilepticus |url=https://www.neurologyindia.com/article.asp?issn=0028-3886;year=2006;volume=54;issue=4;spage=354;epage=358;aulast=Murthy;type=0 |journal=Neurology India |language=en |volume=54 |issue=4 |doi=10.4103/0028-3886.28104 |issn=0028-3886 |pmid=17114841}}</ref>有证据表明，在紧急控制癫痫发作时，咪达唑仑口腔和鼻内给药比[[地西泮|地西泮]]直肠给药更容易且更有效。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Eriksson |first=Kai |last2=Kälviäinen |first2=Reetta |date=2005-11-01 |title=Pharmacologic management of convulsive status epilepticus in childhood |url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1586/14737175.5.6.777 |journal=Expert Review of Neurotherapeutics |volume=5 |issue=6 |doi=10.1586/14737175.5.6.777 |issn=1473-7175}}</ref><ref name="sciencedirect">{{Cite journal |last=Wolfe |first=Timothy R. |last2=Macfarlane |first2=Thomas C. |date=2006-05-01 |title=Intranasal midazolam therapy for pediatric status epilepticus |url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0735675705004134 |journal=The American Journal of Emergency Medicine |language=en |volume=24 |issue=3 |doi=10.1016/j.ajem.2005.11.004 |issn=0735-6757}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Sofou |first=Kalliopi |last2=Kristjánsdóttir |first2=Ragnhildur |last3=Papachatzakis |first3=Nikolaos E. |last4=Ahmadzadeh |first4=Amir |last5=Uvebrant |first5=Paul |date=2009-08 |title=Management of Prolonged Seizures and Status Epilepticus in Childhood: A Systematic Review |url=http://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/0883073809332768 |journal=Journal of Child Neurology |language=en |volume=24 |issue=8 |doi=10.1177/0883073809332768 |issn=0883-0738 |pmid=19332572}}</ref>

=== 程序性镇静 ===
静脉注射咪达唑仑适用于程序镇静（通常与[[鸦片类药物|阿片类药物]]，如[[芬太尼|芬太尼]]联合使用）、术前镇静、[[全身麻醉|全身麻醉]]的诱导以及[[重症医学|重症监护]]室[[呼吸机|通气]]患者的镇静。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Brown |first=Todd B. |last2=Lovato |first2=Luis M. |last3=Parker |first3=Dinora |date=2005-01-01 |title=Procedural sedation in the acute care setting |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15663030/ |journal=American Family Physician |volume=71 |issue=1 |issn=0002-838X |pmid=15663030}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=O’Connor |first=Mark |last2=Bucknall |first2=Tracey |last3=Manias |first3=Elizabeth |date=2010-05-01 |title=Sedation Management in Australian and New Zealand Intensive Care Units: Doctors’ and Nurses’ Practices and Opinions |url=https://doi.org/10.4037/ajcc2009541 |journal=American Journal of Critical Care |volume=19 |issue=3 |doi=10.4037/ajcc2009541 |issn=1062-3264 |pmid=19770414}}</ref>咪达唑仑对内镜检查过程记忆的损害优于地西泮，但[[异丙酚|异丙酚]]恢复时间较快，记忆损害效果较好。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=McQuaid |first=Kenneth R. |last2=Laine |first2=Loren |date=2008-05 |title=A systematic review and meta-analysis of randomized, controlled trials of moderate sedation for routine endoscopic procedures |url=https://www.giejournal.org/article/S0016-5107(07)03354-8/ |journal=Gastrointestinal Endoscopy |volume=67 |issue=6 |doi=10.1016/j.gie.2007.12.046 |issn=0016-5107}}</ref>它是[[重症监护病房|重症监护病房]]（ICU）中最受欢迎的苯二氮卓类药物，因为它的[[生物半衰期|消除半衰期]]短、水溶性和适合连续输注。但对于长期镇静，[[劳拉西泮|劳拉西泮]]作用时间长，首选劳拉西泮，<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Arcangeli |first=A. |last2=Antonelli |first2=M. |last3=Mignani |first3=V. |last4=Sandroni |first4=C. |title=Sedation in PACU: The Role of Benzodiazepines |url=https://www.eurekaselect.com/article/5838 |journal=Current Drug Targets |language=en |volume=6 |issue=7 |doi=10.2174/138945005774574416 |issn=1389-4501 |pmid=16305452}}</ref>
而异丙酚用于ICU镇静较咪达唑仑具有撤机时间短、[[气管插管|气管拔管]]早等优势。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Cosmo |first=G. D. |last2=Congedo |first2=E. |last3=Clemente |first3=A. |last4=Aceto |first4=P. |title=Sedation in PACU: The Role of Propofol |url=https://www.eurekaselect.com/article/5837 |journal=Current Drug Targets |language=en |volume=6 |issue=7 |doi=10.2174/138945005774574425 |issn=1389-4501 |pmid=16305451}}</ref>

咪达唑仑有时用于新生儿重症监护室。 [[婴儿|新生儿]]使用时需要格外小心； 咪达唑仑的使用时间不应超过 72 小时，因为存在快速抗药性反应的风险、发生苯二氮卓类药物戒断综合征的可能性以及神经系统并发症。 由于心血管抑制和神经系统并发症的风险增加，应避免[[推注|弹丸注射]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Rawicz |first=Marcin |date=2008-10 |title=[Recommendations for analgesia and sedation in neonatal intensive care] |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19471072 |journal=Medycyna Wieku Rozwojowego |volume=12 |issue=4 Pt 1 |pmid=19471072}}</ref>咪达唑仑有时也用于接受[[机械通气|机械通气]]的新生儿，尽管吗啡是首选，因为它对这种适应症有更好的安全性。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Bellù |first=Roberto |last2=de Waal |first2=Koert A |last3=Zanini |first3=Rinaldo |date=2008-01-23 |editor-last=Cochrane Neonatal Group |title=Opioids for neonates receiving mechanical ventilation |url=https://www.cochranelibrary.com/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD004212.pub3/ |journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |language=en |volume=2021 |issue=7 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD004212.pub3 |pmc=PMC7388902 |pmid=18254040}}</ref>

使用咪达唑仑进行镇静可用于缓解儿童接受牙科治疗的焦虑和控制行为。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Ashley |first=Paul F |last2=Chaudhary |first2=Mohsin |last3=Lourenço-Matharu |first3=Liege |date=2018-12-17 |editor-last=Cochrane Oral Health Group |title=Sedation of children undergoing dental treatment |url=https://www.cochranelibrary.com/cdsr/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD003877.pub5/ |journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |language=en |volume=2018 |issue=12 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD003877.pub5 |pmc=PMC6517004 |pmid=30566228}}</ref>

=== 烦躁 ===
咪达唑仑与一种抗精神病药物联合使用，适用于与攻击性或失控行为相关的精神分裂症的急性治疗。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Huf |first=Gisele |last2=Alexander |first2=Jacob |last3=Gandhi |first3=Pinky |last4=Allen |first4=Michael H. |date=2016-11-25 |title=Haloperidol plus promethazine for psychosis-induced aggression |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27885664/ |journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |volume=11 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005146.pub3 |issn=1469-493X |pmc=6464403 |pmid=27885664}}</ref>

=== 临终关怀 ===
在[[临终关怀|临终关怀]]的最后阶段，咪达唑仑通常通过皮下注射以低剂量使用，以帮助缓解生命最后几个小时或几天的激动、不安或焦虑。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2005-11 |title=Care of the Dying Pathway (lcp) (Hospital) |url=http://www.mcpcil.org.uk/liverpool-care-pathway/pdfs/LCP%20HOSPITAL%20VERSION%2011%20%28printable%20version%29.pdf |format=PDF |website=The Marie Curie Palliative Care Institute Liverpool |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>本品為-{zh-cn:姑息性; zh-tw:緩和性}-[[缓和镇静|持续深度镇静治疗]]的[[治疗|一线药物]]，為了減輕無效醫療所帶來的痛苦，在臨終階段有時會對患者持續輸注大劑量咪达唑仑，讓病人持續處於麻醉的狀態<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Graeff |first=Alexander De |last2=Dean |first2=Mervyn |date=2007-02-01 |title=Palliative Sedation Therapy in the Last Weeks of Life: A Literature Review and Recommendations for Standards |url=https://www.liebertpub.com/doi/10.1089/jpm.2006.0139 |journal=Journal of Palliative Medicine |volume=10 |issue=1 |doi=10.1089/jpm.2006.0139 |issn=1096-6218 |pmid=17298256}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2015-08-13 |title=National Care of the Dying Audit of Hospitals |url=http://www.rcplondon.ac.uk/projects/outputs/national-care-dying-audit-hospitals |website=RCP London |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>。

