=== 体液检测 ===
可以在血浆、血清或全血中测量咪达唑仑或其主要代谢物 1-羟基咪达唑仑葡糖苷酸的浓度，以监测接受药物治疗的患者的安全性，确认住院患者中毒的诊断，或协助对致命过量病例进行法医调查。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=8th|title=Disposition of toxic drugs and chemicals in man|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/243548756|publisher=Biomedical Publications|date=2008|location=Foster City, Ca|isbn=978-0-9626523-7-0|oclc=243548756|first=Randall C.|last=Baselt}}</ref>

== 相互作用 ==
[[蛋白酶抑制剂_(药理学)|蛋白酶抑制剂]][[奈法唑酮|奈法唑酮]]、[[舍曲林|舍曲林]]、[[葡萄柚|葡萄柚]]、[[氟西汀|氟西汀]]、[[红霉素|红霉素]]、[[地尔硫卓|地尔硫卓]]、[[克拉霉素|克拉霉素]]抑制咪达唑仑的代谢，导致作用延长。[[贯叶连翘|圣约翰草]]、[[利福喷丁|利福喷丁]]、[[利福平|利福平]]、[[利福布丁|利福布丁]]、[[苯妥英|苯妥英]]促进咪达唑仑的代谢，导致作用减弱。[[苯巴比妥|苯巴比妥]]、[[苯妥英|苯妥英]]和[[卡马西平|卡马西平]]镇静抗抑郁药、抗癫痫药、镇静[[抗组胺药|抗组胺药]]、[[阿片类药物|阿片类药物]]、[[抗精神病药|抗精神病药]]和[[乙醇|酒精]]可增强咪达唑仑的镇静作用。<ref name="wiley" />咪达唑仑几乎完全被[[CYP3A4|细胞色素P450-3A4]]代谢。[[阿托伐他汀|阿托伐他汀]]与咪达唑仑一起给药导致咪达唑仑的消除率降低。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Mc Donnell |first=C. G. |last2=Harte |first2=S. |last3=O'Driscoll |first3=J. |last4=O'Loughlin |first4=C. |last5=Van Pelt |first5=F. N. a. M. |last6=Shorten |first6=G. D. |last7=Van Pelt |first7=F. D. |date=2003-09 |title=The effects of concurrent atorvastatin therapy on the pharmacokinetics of intravenous midazolam |url=https://associationofanaesthetists-publications.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1046/j.1365-2044.2003.03339.x |journal=Anaesthesia |volume=58 |issue=9 |doi=10.1046/j.1365-2044.2003.03339.x |issn=0003-2409 |pmid=12911366}}</ref>圣约翰草可降低咪达唑仑的血药浓度。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Hu |first=Zeping |last2=Yang |first2=Xiaoxia |last3=Ho |first3=Paul Chi Lui |last4=Chan |first4=Sui Yung |last5=Heng |first5=Paul Wan Sia |last6=Chan |first6=Eli |last7=Duan |first7=Wei |last8=Koh |first8=Hwee Ling |last9=Zhou |first9=Shufeng |date=2005 |title=Herb-drug interactions: a literature review |url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.2165/00003495-200565090-00005 |journal=Drugs |volume=65 |issue=9 |doi=10.2165/00003495-200565090-00005 |issn=0012-6667 |pmid=15916450}}</ref>葡萄柚汁可减少肠道 3A4 并导致新陈代谢减少和血浆浓度升高。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Arayne |first=M. Saeed |last2=Sultana |first2=Najma |last3=Bibi |first3=Zakia |date=2005-10 |title=Grape fruit juice-drug interactions |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16380358/ |journal=Pakistan Journal of Pharmaceutical Sciences |volume=18 |issue=4 |issn=1011-601X |pmid=16380358}}</ref>

== 药理学 ==
咪达唑仑是一种用于成人的短效苯二氮卓类药物，消除半衰期为 1.5-2.5 小时。<ref name="worldcat4">{{Cite web |title=NEW ZEALAND DATA SHEET |url=https://www.medsafe.govt.nz/profs/datasheet/m/MidazolaminjPfizer.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=New Zealand Medicines and Medical Devices Safety Authority |website=Medsafe |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>在老年人以及幼儿和青少年中，消除半衰期较长。<ref name="wiley2" /><ref>{{Cite book|edition=6th|title=Clinical anesthesia|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/295002335|publisher=Wolters Kluwer/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|date=2009|location=Philadelphia|isbn=978-0-7817-8763-5|oclc=295002335|first=Paul G.|last=Barash}}</ref>咪达唑仑代谢成活性代谢物 α1-羟基咪达唑仑。 年龄相关的缺陷、肾脏和肝脏状况影响咪达唑仑及其活性代谢物的药代动力学因素。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Spina |first=Sean P. |last2=Ensom |first2=Mary H. H. |date=2007-03 |title=Clinical pharmacokinetic monitoring of midazolam in critically ill patients |url=https://accpjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1592/phco.27.3.389 |journal=Pharmacotherapy |volume=27 |issue=3 |doi=10.1592/phco.27.3.389 |issn=0277-0008 |pmid=17316150}}</ref>然而，咪达唑仑的活性代谢物很小，仅占咪达唑仑生物活性的 10%。 咪达唑仑口服吸收不良，只有 50% 的药物进入血液。<ref name="wiley" />咪达唑仑由[[细胞色素P450|细胞色素P450]]（CYP）酶和[[葡糖苷酸|葡糖苷酸]]结合代谢。咪达唑仑的治疗和副作用是由于它对GABA<sub>A</sub>受体的影响；咪达唑仑不直接激活GABA<sub>A</sub>受体，但与其他苯二氮卓类药物一样，它增强神经递质GABA对GABA<sub>A</sub>受体的作用（↑Cl-通道打开的频率），从而导致神经抑制。几乎所有的特性都可以通过苯二氮卓类药物对GABA<sub>A</sub>受体的作用来解释。这导致产生以下药理学特性：镇静、诱导睡眠、减少焦虑、顺行性遗忘、肌肉松弛和抗惊厥作用。<ref name="springer" />

== 历史 ==
咪达唑仑是目前医学上使用的大约35种苯二氮卓类药物之一，<ref name="worldcat5">{{Cite book|edition=2nd ed., reprint|title=Textbook of pharmacology for dental and allied health sciences|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/893585742|publisher=Jaypee Brothers|date=2009|location=India|isbn=81-8448-149-7|oclc=893585742|first=Padmaja|last=Udaykumar}}</ref>由美国[[罗氏|罗氏]]公司的Walser和Fryer于1975年合成。<ref>{{Citation|title=Benzodiapines used as minor tranquilizers|url=https://patents.google.com/patent/US3852461A/en|date=1974-12-03|accessdate=2022-06-19|patent-number=US3852461A|inventor-first=J.|inventor-last=Hester|inventor2-first=M.|inventor2-last=Gall}}</ref>由于其水溶性，发现它比同类药物不太可能引起[[血栓性静脉炎|血栓性静脉炎]]。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=5th|title=Kaplan's cardiac anesthesia|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/60825577|publisher=Elsevier Saunders|date=2006|location=Philadelphia, Pa.|isbn=1-4160-0253-7|oclc=60825577|first=Joel A.|last=Kaplan}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|edition=4th|title=Sedation : a guide to patient management|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/50510926|publisher=Mosby|date=2003|location=St. Louis|isbn=0-323-01226-4|oclc=50510926|first=Stanley F.|last=Malamed}}</ref>咪达唑仑的抗惊厥特性在1970年代后期进行了研究，但直到1990年代它才成为惊厥性癫痫重积状态的有效治疗方法。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Pediatric critical care medicine : basic science and clinical evidence|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/74525568|publisher=Springer|date=2007|location=London|isbn=978-1-84628-463-2|oclc=74525568|first=Derek S.|last=Wheeler|first2=Hector R.|last2=Wong|first3=Thomas P.|last3=Shanley}}</ref>截至2010年，它是麻醉药物中最常用的苯二氮卓类药物。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=2nd|title=Hypertension : a companion to Brenner and Rector's the kidney|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/324998244|publisher=Elsevier Mosby|date=2005|location=Philadelphia|isbn=978-1-4377-1301-5|oclc=324998244|first=Suzanne|last=Oparil|first2=Michael A.|last2=Weber}}</ref>在急性医学中，咪达唑仑比其他苯二氮卓类药物（如[[劳拉西泮|劳拉西泮]]和地西泮）更受欢迎，因为它的持续时间更短，更有效，并且在注射部位引起的疼痛更小。<ref name="worldcat5" />由于其水溶性，咪达唑仑在兽药中也越来越受欢迎。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=9th|title=Veterinary pharmacology and therapeutics.|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/231787193|publisher=Wiley-Blackwell|date=2009|location=Ames, Iowa|isbn=978-0-8138-2061-3|oclc=231787193|first=J. Edmond|last=Riviere|first2=Mark G.|last2=Papich}}</ref>2018 年，据透露，中央情报局考虑在“药物”项目中使用咪达唑仑作为恐怖嫌疑人的“真相血清”。<ref>{{Cite web |title=CIA considered potential truth serum for terror suspects after 9/11 |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/cia-considered-potential-truth-serum-terror-suspects-after-9-11-n935911 |website=NBC News |language=en |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>

