=== 可用性 ===
咪达唑仑在美国以糖浆或注射溶液的形式提供。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Orange Book: Approved Drug Products with Therapeutic Equivalence Evaluations |url=https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/scripts/cder/ob/ |website=FDA |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>

[[罗氏|罗氏]]以-{zh-hans:多美康; zh-hant:導美睡;}-（Dormicum）为商品名销售咪达唑仑，<ref>{{Cite web |title=B017577100 |url=https://www.cth.org.tw/?aid=606&pid=0&page_name=detail&iid=94 |website=天主教耕莘醫療財團法人耕莘醫院 |access-date=2022-06-22}}</ref>白色椭圆形，7.5毫克片剂，每盒两片或三片泡罩条，每盒10片；蓝色椭圆形，15毫克片剂，每盒两片泡罩片，每片10片。药片一侧印有“Roche”字样，另一侧印有药片剂量。Dormicum也有1-、3-和10-ml安瓿瓶，浓度为5 mg/ml。另一家制造商 Novell Pharmaceutical Laboratories 以 Miloz 的形式提供3和5毫升安瓿瓶。咪达唑仑是唯一可用的水溶性苯二氮卓类药物。另一家制造商是 Roxane Laboratories。 口服溶液中的产品，盐酸咪达唑仑糖浆，2 mg/ml 澄清，红色至紫红色糖浆，樱桃味。当可注射溶液缓冲至2.9－3.7的pH值时，它变得可溶。 咪达唑仑也有液体形式。<ref name="wiley" />它可以肌肉内、<ref name="bmj" />静脉内、<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Steib |first=A. |last2=Hausberger |first2=D. |last3=Robillart |first3=A. |last4=Roche |first4=A. |last5=Franckhauser |first5=D. |last6=Dupeyron |first6=J.-P. |date=2006-06 |title=[Anaesthetic considerations for interventional radiology] |url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0750765806000724 |journal=Annales Francaises D'anesthesie Et De Reanimation |volume=25 |issue=6 |doi=10.1016/j.annfar.2006.01.018 |issn=0750-7658 |pmid=16632296}}</ref>鞘内、<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Ho |first=K. M. |last2=Ismail |first2=H. |date=2008-05 |title=Use of intrathecal midazolam to improve perioperative analgesia: a meta-analysis |url=https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/0310057X0803600307 |journal=Anaesthesia and Intensive Care |volume=36 |issue=3 |doi=10.1177/0310057X0803600307 |issn=0310-057X |pmid=18564797}}</ref>鼻内、<ref name="sciencedirect" />口腔<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Beran |first=Roy G. |date=2008-04 |title=An alternative perspective on the management of status epilepticus |url=https://www.epilepsybehavior.com/article/S1525-5050(07)00477-5/ |journal=Epilepsy & Behavior: E&B |volume=12 |issue=3 |doi=10.1016/j.yebeh.2007.12.013 |issn=1525-5050 |pmid=18262847}}</ref>或口服给药。<ref name="wiley" />

=== 法律地位 ===
在荷兰，咪达唑仑是鸦片法第二类药物。 咪达唑仑是《精神药物公约》下的附表 IV 药物。<ref>{{Cite web |title=INCB Psychotropics - Green List |url=https://www.incb.org/incb/en/psychotropics/green-list.html |website=International Narcotics Control Board |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>在英国，咪达唑仑是附表 3/C 类管制药物。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Controlled drugs and drug dependence |url=https://bnf.nice.org.uk/medicines-guidance/controlled-drugs-and-drug-dependence/ |publisher=National Institute for Health and Care Excellence |website=British National Formulary |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>在美国，咪达唑仑（DEA 编号 2884）作为非麻醉剂被列入受控物质法案的附表 IV 清单。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Controlled Substance Schedules |url=https://www.deadiversion.usdoj.gov/schedules/ |website=www.deadiversion.usdoj.gov |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>在中国，咪达唑仑作为第二类精神药品列入《精神药品品种目录》。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2013-11-11 |title=食品药品监管总局　公安部　国家卫生计生委关于公布麻醉药品和精神药品品种目录的通知 |url=https://www.nmpa.gov.cn/xxgk/fgwj/gzwj/gzwjyp/20131111120001419.html |website=国家药品监督管理局 |access-date=2022-06-19}}</ref>

